stic and dynamic in\nnature, as are consumptions by loads which are influenced by factors such as\nlocal temperatures and thermal inertias of facilities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 18 Mar 2018 20:32:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 11 Jun 2019 18:21:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-13"}
