perature show that the annealing rate is different for\ndifferent defects. A naive diffusion model is used to estimate the temperature\ndependencies of the diffusion of the defects in the clusters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Mar 2018 14:28:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-13"}
