o compensate for this error. In the\ntypical examples that were analysed in this study, mean strain errors of around\n60 microstrains were compensated.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Mar 2018 14:10:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 18 Jun 2018 11:28:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-17"}
